TI  - Evaluating transportation infrastructure investment on a regional level: a system dynamics simulation
T2  - SIMULATION-TRANSACTIONS OF THE SOCIETY FOR MODELING AND SIMULATION INTERNATIONAL
LA  - English
KW  - Economics
KW  - employment
KW  - impact evaluation
KW  - system dynamics
KW  - transportation infrastructure investment
