TI  - Dynamic coupling of hydrogeology and human decision-making for sustainable groundwater management in Konya Closed Basin, Türkiye
T2  - JOURNAL OF HYDROLOGY-REGIONAL STUDIES
LA  - English
KW  - Groundwater management
