TI  - System Dynamics Simulation of Policy Synergy Effects: How Tradable Green Certificates and Carbon Emission Trading Shape Electricity Market Sustainability
T2  - APPLIED SCIENCES-BASEL
LA  - English
KW  - tradable green certificate
KW  - carbon emission trading
