TI  - Formation Mechanism and Dynamic Evolution Laws About Unsafe Behavior of New Generation of Construction Workers Based on China's Construction Industry: Application of Grounded Theory and System Dynamics
T2  - FRONTIERS IN PSYCHOLOGY
LA  - English
