AB  - Commercialization of atomic energy is investigated in the aspect of the nanotechnology (NT) application. The atomic nanotechnology has been emerging in the area of science and technology, where the main object is highly efficient production. The marketing innovation is quantified for the profit enhancement using systems thinking which is expressed by the system dynamics method. The feedback and accumulation skills of the simulation could show the higher reliable result of the interested scenarios. The simulation is performed by three aspects which are technological, manpower, and marketing. The output shows the highest point is 312,209 times higher in 2050 than the initial point. This shows the budget increasing for the NT area in industry as well as academics.
