TI  - CONSERVING WATER: COST AND PRODUCTIVITY ANALYSIS OF RESPONSIVE DRIP AND CONVENTIONAL IRRIGATION
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL ENGINEERING AND MANAGEMENT JOURNAL
