TI  - Applying the System of Environmental and Economic Accounts for Water (SEEA-Water) for integrated assessment of water security in an aquifer scale - Case study: Azarshahr aquifer, Iran
T2  - GROUNDWATER FOR SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Water accounting
KW  - System dynamics modelling
KW  - Policy analysis
KW  - Lake Urmia
KW  - FRAMEWORK
