TI  - Sustainable Mechanism of the Entrusted Transportation Management Mode on High-Speed Rail and the Impact of COVID-19: A Case Study of the Beijing-Shanghai High-Speed Rail
T2  - SUSTAINABILITY
LA  - English
KW  - high-speed rail passenger transport
