TI  - EXAMINATION OF THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN THEORY-DRIVEN POLICIES AND ALLOWED LOST-TIME BACK CLAIMS IN WORKERS' COMPENSATION: A SYSTEM DYNAMICS MODEL
T2  - JOURNAL OF MANIPULATIVE AND PHYSIOLOGICAL THERAPEUTICS
LA  - English
